   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Organisational Assessment - Diakonia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">PLEASE REVIEW YOUR ANSWER AS THE QUESTION HAS BEEN CHANGED

Ambassaden har beslutat att genomf&#xF6;ra en organisationsbed&#xF6;mning f&#xF6;r Diakonia i syfte att bed&#xF6;ma den interna kontrollen och f&#xF6;rm&#xE5;ga att f&#xF6;rvalta program. Syftet &#xE4;r att anv&#xE4;nda informationen fr&#xE5;n bed&#xF6;mningen f&#xF6;r att f&#xF6;rst&#xE5; Diakonias svagheter i deras interna kontroller och personalkapacitet samt att komma med en handlingsplan f&#xF6;r f&#xF6;rb&#xE4;ttringar. Handlingsplanen kommer att utg&#xF6;ra en del av dialogfr&#xE5;gorna under den &#xE5;rliga &#xF6;versynen. Uppdraget kommer att genomf&#xF6;ras av EMM Corporate Partners, till den totala kostnaden kronor 66 055. Ambassaden ska betala hela kostnaden.

The Embassy decided to undertake an organisational assessment for Diakonia in order to assess its internal controls and capacity to manage programs. The aim is to use the information from the assessment to understand Diakonia&apos;s weaknesses in thier internal controls and human resource capacity and come up with an action plan for improvements. The action plan will form part of the dialogue issues during the annual review. This assignment will be undertaken by EMM Corporate Partners, a framework agreement firm at the total cost of SEK 66 055. The Embassy shall pay for the whole cost.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To carry out an institutional assessment of internal controls and     management of Diakonia Zambia.</narrative>
  </description>
